Background

		Mr. John B. Replogle has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of Seventh Generation, Inc. since March 7, 2011. Mr. Replogle served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Burt's Bees Inc., from January 2006 to March 2011. Mr. Replogle spent three years at Unilever as General Manager, Skin Care of North America from 2003 to 2006. Mr. Replogle spent eight years with Diageo Plc. Mr. Replogle served as President of Guinness Bass Import Company. He served ... as Managing Director of Guinness Great Britain. He held several other roles in Marketing, Sales and Strategy with Diageo. Mr. Replogle began his career as a Consultant with the Boston Consulting Group. He is a Director of Seventh Generation, Inc. Mr. Replogle has been Director of Cree, Inc. since January 28, 2014. He has been a Trustee of Dartmouth College since April 2010. He serves as Trustee of Ravenscroft School Inc. He served as a Director of Sealy Corporation at Sealy Mattress Company from September 28, 2010 to March 18, 2013. He gained several awards and distinctions, such as the Hansard Scholarship and the Dean's Prize at Dartmouth College. Mr. Replogle holds an MBA from Harvard Business School, graduating with distinction in General and Entrepreneurial Management. Mr. Replogle holds a BA in Political Science from Dartmouth College.Read Full Background




